        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">

        <div class="col-lg-8">

            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-4">

                <div class="card-body p-5">

                    <div class="mb-4">

                        <h3 class="fw-bold text-success">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                            Call Us
                        </h3>

                        <p class="fs-5">
                            +27 67 969 3377
                        </p>

                    </div>

                    <hr />

                    <div class="mb-4">

                        <h3 class="fw-bold text-success">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
                            WhatsApp
                        </h3>

                        <p class="fs-5">
                            +27 67 969 3377
                        </p>

                        <a href="https://wa.me/27XXXXXXXXX"
                           target="_blank"
                           class="btn btn-success rounded-pill px-4">

                            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
                            Chat on WhatsApp

                        </a>

                    </div>

                    <hr />

                    <div class="mb-4">

                        <h3 class="fw-bold text-success">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>
                            Email
                        </h3>

                        <p class="fs-5">
                            Yasthiel24@gmail.com
                        </p>

                    </div>

                    <hr />

                    <div class="text-center mt-5">

                        <i class="fa-solid fa-heart fa-3x text-danger mb-3"></i>

                        <h4 class="fw-bold">
                            Thank You for Choosing Happy Hearts
                        </h4>

                        <p class="text-muted">

                            Every pet deserves a loving home, and we're always
                            happy to help you find the perfect companion.

                        </p>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>
